{
  "id": "S2P01303",
  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "COMMANDS AND PF KEYS",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "HELP"
  },
  "type": "help",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "You may enter multiple commands in a single interaction.  This is called"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "command stacking.+ The commands are executed as if you had entered them"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "one after the other."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Stacked commands must be separated with a delimiter character.  The"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "default delimiter is a semicolon (;).  You may change it via option 0.1."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "COMMAND  change all tct ctc;find abc"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "COMMAND  split;3.4"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "In the first example, two EDIT commands have been stacked.  In the second"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "example, a SPLIT command and an option selection have been stacked (the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "option selection applies to the lower screen created via the SPLIT)."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "PF key definitions may also be equated to a stack of commands."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "PF12  caps off;number on;down 5;hex on"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Press"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+to continue)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
